title: Filibertos Mexican Food
typeOfFood: Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mexican fast food chain in Arizona where you can get a veg burrito. Does not use lard in their beans or tortillas. Rice is made with tomato sauce and spices. Guacamole is vegan. There's a bar with green and red sauce as well as pickled onions and carrots (pickled with jalapeno juice and cold radishes). Basic conventional brands of sodas. Some locations offer iced tea.
